trans-unit.source: Provides a property and methods for writing event and exception information to the application's log listeners.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en egenskap og metoder for skriving hendelses-og unntak til programmets loggen lyttere.

trans-unit.source: The `My.Application.Log` object provides a straightforward entry point from which to access the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]'s logging services.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Application.Log` -objektet har en enkelt inngangspunktet som å få tilgang til den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]for logging av tjenester.

trans-unit.source: The `WriteEntry` and `WriteException` methods write messages to the application's log listeners.
trans-unit.target: Den `WriteEntry` og `WriteException` metoder skrive meldinger til programmets loggen lyttere.

trans-unit.source: The listeners can be configured by the application's configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Lyttere kan konfigureres ved programmets konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Walkthrough: Changing Where My.Application.Log Writes Information](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Working with Application Logs](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [gjennomgang: endre der My.Application.Log skriver informasjon](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [arbeide med programloggen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The `My.Application.Log` object is available only for client applications.
trans-unit.target: Den `My.Application.Log` objektet er bare tilgjengelig for klientprogrammer.
Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists examples of tasks involving the `My.Application.Log` object.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser eksempler på oppgaver som omfatter den `My.Application.Log` objektet.

trans-unit.source: |To|See| |--------|---------| |Write event information to the application's log listeners|[How to: Write Log Messages](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)| |Write exception information to the application's log listeners|[How to: Log Exceptions](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)| |Determine where `My.Application.Log` writes information|[Walkthrough: Determining Where My.Application.Log Writes Information](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)|
trans-unit.target: | Til | Se | |--------|---------| | Skrive hendelsesinformasjon til programmets loggen lyttere | [Slik: skrive loggmeldinger](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)| | Skrive unntaksinformasjon til programmets loggen lyttere | [Slik: logger unntak](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)| | Avgjøre hvor `My.Application.Log` skriver informasjon |[ Gjennomgang: Bestemme der My.Application.Log skriver informasjon](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)|

trans-unit.source: The name to give to the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource*> property object.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på å gi til den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource*>egenskapen objektet.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource*>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"></xref> and adds it to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*> collection.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"> </xref> og legger det til i <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>samlingen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners*>

trans-unit.source: This method creates a new <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener>, sets its name to `FileLog`, and configures it to log messages with severity level <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels> and greater.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden, oppretter en ny <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener>, angir navnet til `FileLog`, og konfigurerer den til å logge meldinger med alvorsgrad <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels>og høyere.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener>

trans-unit.source: The new <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener> object is then added to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Listeners%2A> collection.
The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.%23ctor%2A> calls the method if the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource%2A> property has not been configured.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.%23ctor%2A>kaller metoden hvis den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource%2A>egenskapen er ikke konfigurert.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.TraceSource%2A> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.Log.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The trace source can be configured in the application's configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Sporingskilden kan konfigureres i programmets konfigurasjonsfil.
